With more probable job opportunities that require languages, these skills are essential in a globalized world.
Whatever career anyone chooses, if they have learned a second language, they will have a real advantage in the future with such a lifelong skill.
Being able to communicate directly with people from other countries will automatically put a multilingual person above the competition.
